Title: Office of Justice Programs (OJP) API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the OJP/BJS API. NCVS household population
